                  <lb/>
<notvariant>Heb</notvariant>. 5.9. <quote type="biblical" ana="1 Jn 4.14">He became the Author of eternal<lb/>
Salvation, unto all them that obey him.</quote>
                  <lb/>
1 John 4.14. <quote type="biblical" ana="1 Jn 4.14">We have seen, and do<lb/>
<normalised orig="testifie" auto="true">testify</normalised>, that the Father sent the Son to be<lb/>
the Saviour of the World.</quote>
                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>
               </p>
            </sp>
            <sp who="a">
               <p>Quest. How <normalised orig="dost" auto="true">do</normalised> thou prove, that Salvation<lb/>
