                  <lb/>
1 John 5.12. <quote type="biblical" ana="1 Jn 5.12">He that <normalised orig="hath" auto="true">has</normalised> the Son,<lb/>
                     <pb n="15"/>
                     <lb/>
<normalised orig="hath" auto="true">has</normalised> Life: and he that <normalised orig="hath" auto="true">has</normalised> not the Son,<lb/>
<normalised orig="hath" auto="true">has</normalised> not Life.</quote> 1 <normalised orig="Jn" auto="true">In</normalised> 5.12<lb/>
               </p>
            </sp>
            <sp who="a">
               <p>Quest. How <normalised orig="dost" auto="true">do</normalised> thou prove, that<lb/>
Jesus is the Christ?<lb/>
               </p>
            </sp>
            <sp who="b">
               <p><notvariant>Answ</notvariant>. From Mat. 16.16. <quote type="biblical" ana="Mt 16.16">Thou art<lb/>
