            </sp>
            <sp who="b">
               <p><notvariant>Answ</notvariant>. From John 1.1. <quote type="biblical" ana="Jn 1.1">In the beginning<lb/>
                     <pb n="16"/>
                     <lb/>
was the Word, and the Word was with<lb/>
