                  <lb/>
Luke 1.35. <quote type="biblical" ana="Lk 1.35">The holy Ghost shall come<lb/>
upon thee: and the power of the Highest<lb/>
shall overshadow thee: therefore also that<lb/>
                     <lb/>
                    <fw type="pageNum">C</fw>
                     <pb n="17"/>
                     <lb/>
Holy thing which shall be born of thee, shall<lb/>
