                  <lb/>
Gal. 4.4. <quote type="biblical" ana="Gal 4.4">God sent forth his Son made<lb/>
of a Woman.</quote>
                  <lb/>
<notvariant>Heb</notvariant>. 2.16. <quote type="biblical" ana="Heb 2.16">Verily he took not upon him<lb/>
