               </p>
            </sp>
            <pb n="18"/>
            <sp who="b">
               <p><notvariant>Answ</notvariant>. From Mat. 1.22, 23. <quote type="biblical" ana="Mt 1.22-23">Now all<lb/>
this was done, that it might be fulfilled<lb/>
