                  <lb/>
1 Cor. 1.10. <quote type="biblical" ana="1 Cor 1.10">I <choice ana="illegible">
                        <sic>b*s*ch</sic>
                        <corr>beseech</corr>
                     </choice> you, brethren, by<lb/>
the name of our Lord Jesus Christ, that <normalised orig="ye" auto="true">you</normalised><lb/>
all speak the same thing, and that there be no<lb/>
