                        <sic/>
                        <corr/>
                     </choice> be perfectly<lb/>
<normalised orig="joyned" auto="true">joined</normalised> together in the same mind, and in the<lb/>
same judgment.</quote>
                  <lb/>
1 John 1.7. <quote type="biblical" ana="1 Jn 1.7">If we walk in the light, as<lb/>
he is in the light, we have fellowship one<lb/>
with another.</quote>
                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>
               </p>
            </sp>
            <pb n="27"/>
            <sp who="a">
               <p>Quest. What <normalised orig="believest" auto="true">believe</normalised> thou concerning<lb/>
the tenth Article of the Creed,<lb/>
                  <lb/>
The forgiveness of Sins?<lb/>
               </p>
            </sp>
            <sp who="b">
               <p><notvariant>Answ</notvariant>. I believe that in the Christian<lb/>
