                  <lb/>
<notvariant>Eph</notvariant>. 1.7. <quote type="biblical" ana="Eph 1.7">In whom we have redemption<lb/>
through his blood, the forgiveness of sins,<lb/>
according to the riches of his Grace.</quote>
                  <lb/>
John 20.23. <quote type="biblical" ana="Jn 20.23">Whose <notvariant>soever</notvariant> sins <normalised orig="ye" auto="true">you</normalised> remit,<lb/>
