                  <lb/>
2 Cor. 4.14. <quote type="biblical" ana="2 Cor 4.14">Knowing that he which<lb/>
raised up the Lord Jesus, shall raise up us also<lb/>
by Jesus.</quote>
                  <lb/>
1 <normalised orig="Thes" auto="true">These</normalised>. 4.14. <quote type="biblical" ana="1 Thess 4.14">If we believe that Jesus<lb/>
died, and rose again; even so them also which<lb/>
