                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>
               </p>
            </sp>
            <sp who="a">
               <p>Quest. How are the Wicked to be <normalised orig="dispos'd" auto="true">disposed</normalised><lb/>
of hereafter?<lb/>
               </p>
            </sp>
            <sp who="b">
               <p><notvariant>Answ</notvariant>. They are to be <normalised orig="banish'd" auto="true">banished</normalised> from<lb/>
the presence of God; and tormented<lb/>
eternally in Hell, with the Devil, and<lb/>
his Angels.<lb/>
               </p>
            </sp>
            <sp who="a">
               <p>Quest. How is this <normalised orig="prov'd" auto="true">proved</normalised> from Scripture?<lb/>
               </p>
